title: Cheesy Caramelized Onion Dip
directions: Heat oil in large skillet on medium heat. Add onions; cook 13 to 15 min. or until tender and golden brown, stirring frequently. Remove from heat. Stir in cheese and mayo.
Spread onto bottom of 9-inch pie plate sprayed with cooking spray.
Bake 45 to 55 min. or until golden brown. Let stand 5 min. before serving. Sprinkle with chives.
ingredients: 1 pkg. (8 oz.) KRAFT Shredded Pepper Jack Cheese
1-1/2 cups KRAFT Light Mayo Reduced Fat Mayonnaise
